summary: My second commission house.  This time made for a friend.  It is intentionally empty, so you can fill it as you like.
descriptionHtml:
My second commission house.  This time made for a friend who doesn\'t want his name to be shown here.  It is intentionally empty, so you can fill it as you like.

Message me if you want a house of your own.  I can do any type of house in any location on the map.  I ask for nothing more than for you to spread the word in return.
author: FlyingElephant
